). Wealthy Romans escaped the summer heat in the hills round Rome, especially around <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../997/1553997.xml">
Frascati</link> (<it>cf</it> <structure wordnetid="104341686" confidence="0.8">
<building wordnetid="102913152" confidence="0.8">
