 had three or four, of which the example near Laurentium is the best known from his descriptions.</p>
<p>

The late <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../816/25816.xml">
Roman Republic</link></country>
 witnessed an explosion of villa construction in Italy, especially in the years following the dictatorship of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../672/239672.xml">
Sulla</link>. In <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.8">
<region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
