<p>

The Empire contained many kinds of villas, not all of them lavishly appointed with <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../309/61309.xml">
mosaic</link> floors and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../144/11144.xml">
fresco</link>es. Some were pleasure houses such as those— like <structure wordnetid="104341686" confidence="0.8">
<building wordnetid="102913152" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<villa wordnetid="104535524" confidence="0.8">
