<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../994/25994.xml">
Roman legion</link></military_unit>
s in Germany were a feature of the southern Iberian province of <region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<administrative_district wordnetid="108491826" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
